snippet.description:
OUT NOW: https://stefannofornari-games.itch.io/dont-give-up-on-me

A confession goes wrong in multiple ways and days, but you cannot give up!

Yorokobi Akihiko has a simple yet annoying problem: He's madly in love with Yoru Aoi. But it seems like the universe conspires against him! No matter what, something goes wrong when he's trying to confess his feelings! Even so, he won't give up that easily!

Don't Give Up On Me! is a free romance-comedy visual novel about a simple love confession going wrong in the most unpredictable, absurd and insane ways ever imagined.

- 28,000+ words;
- 3 special CGs;
- 9 different scenarios;
- 4 dumb characters;
- A sweet and chaotic love story;
- A cute raccoon;
- English and Brazilian Portuguese versions!

Available in Windows, Mac, Linux and Android.

Written by Stefanno Fornari and Ryuzi_nea.
Art and Design by Ryuzi_nea.
Music, Sound and Programming by Stefanno Fornari.
Created by Stefannofornari Games.

